00:04:59.100 --> 00:05:00.565
Dol z moje stene!

00:05:00.567 --> 00:05:02.233
Lahko mi uspe.

00:05:02.235 --> 00:05:04.136
Dol z moje vrvi
in nazaj v vrsto!

00:05:09.108 --> 00:05:12.511
Stegni roke, Leavey!
Stegni roke!

00:05:12.512 --> 00:05:16.314
Hočem videti stegnjene roke!
Tam zunaj boš umrla! Me slišiš?

00:05:16.317 --> 00:05:18.617
Po diplomi se lepo imej.

00:05:18.619 --> 00:05:20.819
