Izgini mi izpred oči.

00:05:22.656 --> 00:05:25.624
Naprej, marš!

00:05:25.625 --> 00:05:28.526
Leva! Leva!

00:05:28.528 --> 00:05:31.329
Leva, leva, leva!

00:05:31.331 --> 00:05:33.499
Leva! Naprej, marš!

00:05:34.800 --> 00:05:36.769
Leva! Leva!

00:05:47.880 --> 00:05:50.415
Pozor! Mirno!

00:05:51.451 --> 00:05:54.586
Vod 5004, voljno!

00:05:56.055 --> 00:05:57.590
Ja, gospa!

00:06:16.141 --> 00:06:17.877
Megan?

00:06:17.879 --> 00:06:19.879
Živjo!

00:06:19.880 --> 00:06:22.747
Živjo.
-Živjo! Uspelo nama je!

00:06:22.750 --> 00:06:24.983
No, ni vama. Pravzaprav
sta zamudila, ampak...

00:06:24.985 --> 00:06:27.987
